subject: Basketball
lead_paragraph: Andre Iguodala scored 24 points, Willie Green had 20 and the Philadelphia 76ers never trailed last night in a 99-94 victory against the Phoenix Suns, who lost on the road to an Eastern Conference team for the first time.
